{"tid":2388641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO全面進場！英國政府開放BNO簽證通道　讓合資格港人網上預約","createTime":"2021-01-31T09:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:49:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0a7a107b759722661f1062360b6ee45efc952e","tid":2388641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573304-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573304-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=72d713ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573304-20210131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fdeecf48\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573304-20210131.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府在香港時間下午5時起，開放BNO簽證通道，讓合乎資格的港人，透過網上預約，申請簽證。<br />\n<br />\n在英國政府的網站列明申請條件必須以香港作為永久居住地，擬備所需文件，並預約到簽證申請中心提供生物認證資料。當按下「申請」鍵後，需要輸入申請和提供生物識別信息的國家或者地區。申請人之後要輸入電郵和設定密碼，設立帳戶作日後更改資料等用途。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府不滿英國違背《中英聯合聲明》承諾，宣布今日起不再承認BNO作為旅行證件和身份證明，並保留採取進一步措施的權利。<br />\n<br />\n而特區政府表示，全面配合國家的反制措施，今日起不承認BNO作為有效旅行證件和身分證明。"},{"pid":"ea8bb511465ede06870a48f89f0ea3d9b8cba9fd","tid":2388641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd37f0f5b96a95d92a7ccef59313e78e5e139c9","tid":2388641,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixHXPLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixHXPLU.jpg&h=ffa41dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLike &amp; Share<br />\n<br />\n多謝英國政府<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/557636791288208/posts/1292663261118887/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F557636791288208%2Fposts%2F1292663261118887%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=ea4e4816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/557636791288208/posts/1292663261118887/?d=n</a>"}]}